{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about/procurement","content_id":"63fbccfd-4167-429a-a5f9-dd0aa2160c91","description":"Information for those looking to become a supplier or contractor for UK Fusion Energy (UKFE).","details":{"attachments":[{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"communications.step@ukifs.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"69b92fb6a564b64fbe35aadc","filename":"ukfe-information-for-suppliers.docx"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document","file_size":50790,"filename":"ukfe-information-for-suppliers.docx","id":"9188252","title":"UK Fusion Energy: Information for suppliers","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b92fb6a564b64fbe35aadc/ukfe-information-for-suppliers.docx"},{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"communications.step@ukifs.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"69cbc33f2d120d9d5ec0f31d","filename":"UKFE_PO_Terms__March_2026___2_.docx"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document","file_size":61003,"filename":"UKFE_PO_Terms__March_2026___2_.docx","id":"9218124","title":"UKFE Standard Purchase Order Terms and Conditions","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69cbc33f2d120d9d5ec0f31d/UKFE_PO_Terms__March_2026___2_.docx"}],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"routes-to-market\">Routes to market</h2>\n\n<p>We use a number of methods to purchase goods and services. The approach taken will depend on the contract value, type of product/service, the complexity of the requirement and the duration of the agreement.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"direct-orders--low-value-off-the-shelf-purchases-current-threshold-20000\">Direct orders – Low value off the shelf purchases (current threshold &lt;£20,000)</h3>\n\n<p>Demonstration of value for money is required as well as 3 quotations provided. A simple purchase order with terms and conditions is issued for low value purchases. See <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69cbc33f2d120d9d5ec0f31d/UKFE_PO_Terms__March_2026___2_.docx\">UKFE Standard Purchase Order Terms and Conditions</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">MS Word Document</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">59.6 KB</span>)</span> for more information.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"information-for-suppliers\">Information for suppliers</h2>\n\n<p>Please see <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b92fb6a564b64fbe35aadc/ukfe-information-for-suppliers.docx\">UK Fusion Energy: Information for suppliers</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">MS Word Document</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">49.6 KB</span>)</span> for general guidance on becoming a supplier to UK Fusion Energy.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"procurement-portal\">Procurement portal</h2>\n\n<p>Visit the UK Fusion Energy procurement portal at <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://ukifs.delta-esourcing.com/\">https://ukifs.delta-esourcing.com/</a>. Through this platform, you can explore current procurement opportunities and stay informed about upcoming tenders.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"contact-the-procurement-team\">Contact the procurement team</h2>\n\n<p>Contact the UK Fusion Energy procurement team at: <a href=\"mailto:operationalprocurement.step@ukifs.uk\">operationalprocurement.step@ukifs.uk</a></p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:01:11Z"}],"headers":[{"headers":[{"id":"direct-orders--low-value-off-the-shelf-purchases-current-threshold-20000","level":3,"text":"Direct orders – Low value off the shelf purchases (current threshold <£20,000)"}],"id":"routes-to-market","level":2,"text":"Routes to market"},{"id":"information-for-suppliers","level":2,"text":"Information for suppliers"},{"id":"procurement-portal","level":2,"text":"Procurement portal"},{"id":"contact-the-procurement-team","level":2,"text":"Contact the procurement team"}],"organisation":"e2193247-d27f-4509-b0ae-45abbc391cc1","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"procurement","first_published_at":"2026-03-31T14:01:12+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about/procurement","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about/procurement","base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about/procurement","content_id":"63fbccfd-4167-429a-a5f9-dd0aa2160c91","document_type":"procurement","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-03-31T13:01:11Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Procurement at UKFE","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about/procurement","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1472","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy","base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy","content_id":"e2193247-d27f-4509-b0ae-45abbc391cc1","details":{"acronym":"UKFE","brand":"department-for-business-innovation-skills","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"UK Fusion Energy"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"UK Fusion Energy","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy","withdrawn":false}],"taxons":[{"api_path":"/api/content/business-and-industry/scientific-research-and-development","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/business-and-industry/scientific-research-and-development","base_path":"/business-and-industry/scientific-research-and-de